{"tid":2408783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18大學學生會籲習帝尊重緬人意願勿承認軍政府","createTime":"2021-02-15T09:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T09:09:47.000Z","uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf4cdb4c22118dcccf64830d198d00f167154b7","tid":2408783,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"緬甸2月1日發生軍事政變後，當地局勢周日轉趨緊張，最大城市仰光街頭出現裝甲車，北部的密支那更據報有軍警開槍，但仰光周一再次有大批市民無懼軍方威嚇及中止互聯網，再次上街反對政變。緬甸傳媒報道，該國18間大學的學生會日前向中國國家主席習近平致公開信，促請中國尊重緬甸人民意願，不應承認軍方統治。路透社報道，國務資政昂山素姬將最少被還柙至本月17日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210215/YBC4FZFTQREIFAYC2AK7FXVTME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FYBC4FZFTQREIFAYC2AK7FXVTME%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=01bf4a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FYBC4FZFTQREIFAYC2AK7FXVTME%2F&h=ba9384c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210215/YBC4FZFTQREIFAYC2AK7FXVTME/</a>"},{"pid":"9ac930f8b89e235a6a48c9019b0d84c769306e59","tid":2408783,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHGsdjo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHGsdjo.gif&h=5fd791e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tNbEZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tNbEZy.jpg&h=d769df9e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}